Name: Average time from Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Request Payment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Total time spent on Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time for cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Minimum time from Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION to Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time between Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE in cases of re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR in cases where re-submission occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Payment Handled in cases where payment is eventually made
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time for a case to be closed after Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases with Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR as the final activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and the end of case where activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR occurs

Name: Average waiting time before Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR after Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION in cases of appeal or review
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases involving Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR compared to cases without it
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR to Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE in cases of mutual rejection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by SUPERVISOR' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
